ontent/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Blink-182">Blink-182</a>宣布了他们最新产品“One More Time…第 2 部分”的详细信息和发布日期。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blink-182-one-more-time-review-lyrics-tracklist-3517188">Blink-182 –“再来一次”评论：一次令人惊讶的感人重聚</a></strong></li></ul><p>他们的 2023 年 LP &#39;<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blink-182-one-more-time-review-lyrics-tracklist-3517188">One More Time</a> &#39; 的扩展版将于 9 月 6 日发行，您可以<a href="https://columbiarecords.us8.list-manage.com/track/click?u=b0e73cdbcc097fa26b1ca3940&amp;id=87e04a6169&amp;e=db291b2d3b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>。 《One More Time… Part 2》将包括八首全新曲目，其中第一首《All In My Head》将于周五（8 月 23 日）发行。</p><p> 《再来一次……第二部分》将以各种物理格式以及流媒体平台上的数字形式提供。限量版 2xLP 完整豪华压印在蓝色球彩色乙烯基上。它将包含所有 27 首曲目以及折叠封面和印刷插页。 </p><figure id="attachment_3785047" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3785047" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3785047" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Blink-182“One More time ... Part 2”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2006" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x802.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1396.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Blink-182-One-More-time-.-Part-2-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1071.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3785047" class="wp-caption-text"> Blink-182 “One More time … Part 2”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Blink-182 &#39;One More Time... Part 2&#39; 曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.《国歌第三部分》</strong><br /> <strong>2.“与我共舞”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“坠入爱河”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“害怕”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“再来一次”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“比你知道的更多”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“把它关掉！”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“当我们年轻的时候”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“磨边”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“你不知道自己拥有什么”</strong><br /> <strong>11.“眨眼波”</strong><br /> <strong>12.“坏消息”</strong><br /> <strong>13.“伤害（插曲）”</strong><br /> <strong>14.“松节油”</strong><br /> <strong>15.“他妈的脸”</strong><br /> <strong>16.“另一面”</strong><br /> <strong>17.“别打扰我”</strong><br /> <strong>18.“再见”</strong><br /> <strong>19.《童年》</strong><br /> <strong>20.“没有乐趣”</strong><br /> <strong>21.“一切都在我的脑海里”</strong><br /> <strong>22.“无法回去”</strong><br /> <strong>23.“每隔一个周末”</strong><br /> <strong>24.“每个地方的每个人”</strong><br /> <strong>25.“如果你从未离开”</strong><br /> <strong>26.《一夜情》</strong><br /> <strong>27.“带我进去”</strong></p><p>将提供 1xLP 压制，其中将首次收录 10 首歌曲的黑胶唱片，其中包括 8 首新歌和 2 首以前仅以数字形式提供的奖励曲目。最后，还有限量版豪华版，仅压在特殊的红色火箭色乙烯基上，带有折叠夹克和印刷插页。您可以<a href="https://blink182merch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">从</a>乐队的官方网站预订黑胶唱片。</p><p>就在鼓手<a href="/artists/Travis-Barker">特拉维斯·巴克（Travis Barker）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-barker-update-blink-182-one-more-time-part-2-3784721">在推特上发布“《One More Time Part 2》已为你们混音并制作母带”的一天后，宣布了该专辑的扩展版。</a>此更新是<a href="https://x.com/travisbarker/status/1815466334395994312" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在他于 7 月份首次调侃“谁准备好观看‘再来一次第二部分’”之后</a>发布的。</p><p>上周，在流行朋克偶像登上密歇根州底特律的舞台之前，粉丝们发现一支商品乐队从扬声器中演奏着看似新的音乐。<a href="https://x.com/blink182italia/status/1823248865648140361" target="_blank" rel="noopener">货车侧面写着8月19日的日期</a>，暗示着一项重大公告。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C87nWVnSSox/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 